review.reviewBody: Authentic Chinese/Cantonese cuisine that's absolutely delicious. I had the Deep Fried Squid With Spicy Salt & Chili (regular size) and the portion size and taste are so good.
I love the egg 223. 蠔皇北菇玉子豆腐 /  Chinese Mushroom & Egg Tofu In Oyster Sauce so much!!!! absolutely my favorite.
Excellent, authentic Chinese food. Fried rice and soup are what you can expect to have in  China. Would order again.
Their not consistent with their soups, sometime I receive noodles, and others I don't

The soup eas bland and flavouess.
The deep fried squid was overcooked, tough to eat,. Like rubber.
